<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلِ الشَّاعِرِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَمَا لِلنَّوَى لَا بَارَكَ اللَّهُ فِي النَّوَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَعَهْدُ النَّوَى عِنْدَ الْفِرَاقِ ذَمِيمُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَسَمِعَ الْأَصْمَعِيُّ مَنْ يُنْشِدُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَمَا لِلنَّوَى جَدَّ النَّوَى قَطَعَ النَّوَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>كَذَاكَ النَّوَى قَطَّاعَةٌ لِلْقَرَائِنِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ:</span> لَوْ قُيِّضَ لِهَذَا الْبَيْتِ شَاةٌ لَأَتَتْ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثُ:</span> الِاسْتِلْذَاذُ بِذِكْرِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">كَقَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَبِالْحَقِّ أنزلناه وبالحق نزل}</span> إِنْ كَانَ الْحَقُّ الثَّانِي هُوَ الْأَوَّلُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلِهِ:</span> <span class="c3">{مَنْ كَانَ يُرِيدُ الْعِزَّةَ فَلِلَّهِ الْعِزَّةُ جَمِيعًا}</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَأَوْرَثَنَا الْأَرْضَ نَتَبَوَّأُ مِنَ الْجَنَّةِ حيث نشاء}</span> وَلَمْ يَقُلْ: <span class="c1">"مِنْهَا"</span> وَلِهَذَا عَدَلَ عَنْ ذِكْرِ الْأَرْضِ إِلَى الْجَنَّةِ وَإِنْ كَانَ الْمُرَادُ بِالْأَرْضِ الْجَنَّةَ وَلِلَّهِ دَرُّ الْقَائِلِ:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كَرِّرْ عَلَى السَّمْعِ مِنِّي أَيُّهَا الْحَادِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ذِكْرَ الْمَنَازِلِ وَالْأَطْلَالِ وَالنَّادِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَا مُطْرِبِي بِحَدِيثِ مَنْ سَكَنَ الْغَضَى<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>هجت الهوى وقدحت في حراق<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>إن كررت حَدِيثَكَ يَا مُهَيِّجَ لَوْعَتِي<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>إِنَّ الْحَدِيثَ عَنِ الحبيب تلاق<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>